long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
An extension that either redirects you from arXiv, bioRxiv, medRxiv, or HuggingFace paper pages to the corresponding article on Synthical (if redirection is enabled in the settings), or displays a button on the page for direct access to the Synthical article.

Source code: https://github.com/mixeden/synthical-chrome-extension/
